<item>
            <title>[DERBY-3742] Move test code from CompressedNumber to a unit test</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-3742</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The class org.apache.derby.iapi.services.io.CompressedNumber contains a significant amount of test code. This code should be moved into a unit test to reduce the footprint of the product jars and to ensure that the code is tested in the regression tests. The test code is located in the methods checkInt(), checkLong() and main().&lt;/p&gt;</description>
